<section class="section" id="story_section">
  <%= page_nav_colour_swap_background %>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Love at first bite</h1>
    <h2>The story of delicious nachos</h2>
    <p>At a Museum of Anthropology staff party on July 7, 2010, Nicholas Jakobsen put a tray of the strangest nachos Brianne Phaff had ever seen down in front of her. That tray sparked a conversation, and by the end of the night, Nick had fooled Bre into giving him her number. Nearly five years later, on Christmas Day, 2014, Nick asked Bre to marry him.</p>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <span class="nick_avatar"></span>
        <span class="subtitle">Nick</span>
        <ul class="list-unstyled one_at_a_time_list" data-behaviour="one-at-a-time-list">
          <li>... eats ghost peppers without flinching.</li>
          <li>... regularly wakes up at 6am on Saturdays to run 16km.</li>
          <li>... has attended the Sasquatch music festival for 8 years in a row.</li>
          <li>... still goes trick-or-treating on Halloween.</li>
          <li>... climbed a mountain in Nepal when he was 17.</li>
          <li>... does a really great Arnold Schwarzenegger impression.
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <span class="bre_avatar"><span class="bre_avatar_background"></span></span>
        <span class="subtitle">Bre</span>
        <ul class="list-unstyled one_at_a_time_list" data-behaviour="one-at-a-time-list">
          <li>... is originally from Calgary. She hates country music but loves the rodeo.</li>
          <li>... helped excavate a Neanderthal skull one summer in Spain.</li>
          <li>... regularly uses baking as a form of procrastination.
          <li>... can’t resist dancing to 80’s music.</li>
          <li>... once had dinner with Tongan royalty.</li>
          <li>... is a sucker for Tarantino movies.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

